flask-smart-talk/
│
├── app.py                # Main Flask app (handles routes like login, register)
├── requirements.txt      # List of Python dependencies (Flask, etc.)
├── smarttalk.db          # SQLite database (auto-created if missing)
├── README.md             # Instructions on running & deploying
│
├── templates/            # All HTML pages
│   ├── index.html        # Home page
│   ├── about.html        # About page
│   ├── contact.html      # Contact page
│   ├── login.html        # Login page
│   ├── register.html     # Register page
│   ├── dashboard.html    # After login page (Home, Chat, Notifications, Post)
│
└── static/
    └── style.css         # CSS styling
